The Pelican Brief is a 1993 American legal political thriller based on the novel of the same name by John Grisham .
Directed by Alan J. Pakula , the film stars Julia Roberts in the role of young law student Darby Shaw and Denzel Washington as Washington Herald reporter Gray Grantham .
Music was composed by James Horner .
This was the last film to feature Pakula as a producer and writer before his death .